b9c5d933050e"],

Cell["\<\
Now that we have gone through the postulates of quantum mechanics, we have \
our first chance to apply everything that we have learned so far to evaluate \
a model system.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.808741732722314*^9, 
  3.8087417752475333`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9a6249e2-3263-4500-8523-\
066a88f64229"],

