29e503a8e21d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "We\[CloseCurlyQuote]ll come back to the implications of equation (16) in a \
moment, but we still haven\[CloseCurlyQuote]t finished solving for \[Psi](",
 StyleBox["x",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " ). Up to this point, we have found that"
}], "Text",
