7566e27d3eba"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "where we are now noting that there is a different wavefunction for each \
value of ",
 StyleBox["n",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ". Substituting equation (14) into equation (17), we find that "
}], "Text",
