 "We don\[CloseCurlyQuote]t have any more boundary conditions to help us \
constrain the value of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox[
   StyleBox["c",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8078710533079896`*^9, 3.8078710768513994`*^9}, {
    3.8078712094225693`*^9, 3.8078712100284305`*^9}, {3.808745227603225*^9, 
    3.8087452448174677`*^9}, {3.8087452815607195`*^9, 3.808745289480257*^9}, 
    3.8087453853954077`*^9, {3.8087455156197157`*^9, 
    3.8087455158582363`*^9}, {3.808745546821913*^9, 3.8087455791958895`*^9}, {
    3.8087456910028687`*^9, 3.8087456996212797`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "c069112a-0e4a-4b16-9ccf-0cc93a342be6"],
 ", but we do have another condition that we can apply. Remember that, since \
we have a probabilistic interpretation of the wavefunction, the wavefunction \
must obey the condition"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.808747209400695*^9, 3.8087472302466135`*^9}, {
  3.80874727332065*^9, 
