Cell["\<\
To understand why there are multiple features here instead of just one, we \
have to discuss a great deal more about molecular spectroscopy. Also, this \
paper was published in 1984, but people were still trying to accurately \
predict the spectrum in 2019 (the red in the figure below is the predicted \
spectrum):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8093603451747875`*^9, 3.809360382358081*^9}, {
  3.8093605556397114`*^9, 3.8093605692306814`*^9}, {3.809360608347662*^9, 
